import React from "react";
import {
  Container,
  Header,
  List,
  Grid,
  Segment,
  Placeholder
} from "semantic-ui-react";

const PlaceholderLoad = () => (
  <Container style={{ margin: 20 }}>
    <Grid columns={1} stackable>
      <Grid.Column>
        <Segment raised>
          <Placeholder>
            <Placeholder.Header image>
              <Placeholder.Line />
              <Placeholder.Line />
            </Placeholder.Header>
            <Placeholder.Paragraph>
              <Placeholder.Line length="medium" />
              <Placeholder.Line length="short" />
            </Placeholder.Paragraph>
          </Placeholder>
        </Segment>
      </Grid.Column>

      <Grid.Column>
        <Segment raised>
          <Placeholder>
            <Placeholder.Header image>
              <Placeholder.Line />
              <Placeholder.Line />
            </Placeholder.Header>
            <Placeholder.Paragraph>
              <Placeholder.Line length="medium" />
              <Placeholder.Line length="short" />
            </Placeholder.Paragraph>
          </Placeholder>
        </Segment>
      </Grid.Column>

      <Grid.Column>
        <Segment raised>
          <Placeholder>
            <Placeholder.Header image>
              <Placeholder.Line />
              <Placeholder.Line />
            </Placeholder.Header>
            <Placeholder.Paragraph>
              <Placeholder.Line length="medium" />
              <Placeholder.Line length="short" />
            </Placeholder.Paragraph>
          </Placeholder>
        </Segment>
      </Grid.Column>
    </Grid>
  </Container>
);
export default PlaceholderLoad;
